		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">Aaron Loeb is Director of Business Development and Producer at Planet Moon Studios, makers of MDK, Giants: Citizen Kabuto, Armed & Dangerous, and the upcoming PSP game, Infected. Before joining Planet Moon, Aaron was one of the co-founders of the UGO network, served as editor-in-chief for Next Generation Online until its closure and created the daily web magazine, Daily Radar, where he was Editorial Director until its untimely demise. He was also one of the creators of the Game Critics Awards for the Best of E3 and served for five years as the chairman of those awards.</span></td>
